collation.signatures:
Traces of black ink, probably of European numerals, in the upper left corner of
                           fols. 13r,  and 21r, .
                              5, cut off, in the upper left corner of 32r, ;
                              Traces of a cut off European numeral, probably 6, in the upper left corner of 36r, ;
                             very small remains of black ink in the upper left corner of 40r,  and 48r,  ;
                              Traces of a cut off European numeral, probably 9, in the upper left corner of 56r, ;
                              possibly remains of Ethiopian quire mark decoration on in the upper left corner of 86r, 
                              and 97r.
